lastfm.summary: Psychedelic/space rock band LIQUID VISIONS was founded in Berlin at the turn of the year 1994/95 by Hans-Peter Ringholz (guitar, vocals), Dave Schmidt (aka Sula Bassana) on bass, Robert Terkhany (guitar, vocals) and drummer Markus Rometsch. Over the years the band saw a bunch of line-up changes and developed the sound which basically is a blend of garage/fuzz rock and spacey trips in combination with a lightshow concept when playing live. The band soon started playing gigs. Read more on Last.fm.
lastfm.title: Pink Cloud
